## Wrong affinity Page
wrongAffinity.title=Enrol with the safety & security service
wrongAffinity.heading=Set up a new account
wrongAffinity.paragraph.asIndividual=You have signed in with a individual account. To enrol with safety and security you need an Organisation account.
wrongAffinity.paragraph.asOrganisation=You have signed in with a agent account. To enrol with safety and security you need an Organisation account.
wrongAffinity.instructionsToProceed=You need to:
wrongAffinity.instructionsToProceed.1=Create an Organisation account on the Government Gateway website
wrongAffinity.instructionsToProceed.2=Sign in to HMRC with the new sign in details
wrongAffinity.instructionsToProceed.3=Enrol with safety and security using the new account
wrongAffinity.signOutToGGW=Sign out and create ''Organisation'' account

